1
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,200
Naan.

2
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:03,560
Come on, kids.

3
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:05,580
Come here and have some barbecue.

4
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:07,320
How about some barbecue?

5
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,560
Okay.

6
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:09,640
Barbecue.

7
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:10,840
Be careful,

8
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,120
it's hot.

9
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,920
Mr. Yin, this way.

10
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,010
It has already started.

11
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:31,880
Look.

12
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:34,600
Grandpa Bate.

13
00:01:35,080 --> 00:01:35,880
Grandpa Bate.

14
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:37,380
Mr. Yin is here.

15
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:38,560
Welcome.

16
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,920
Today is Corban Festival. Yes.

17
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,050
We are so happy. Yes.

18
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,280
Let's go, Mr. Yin.

19
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,800
Come on, let's dance.

20
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:45,920
We'll head over first.

21
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:46,520
Dance.

22
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,880
Thank you, Aunt Guli.

23
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:08,360
You're welcome. Eat up, everyone.

24
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,000
Okay.

25
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,180
Secretary, where is Ren Zhen?

26
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:15,720
She went back to change into her new clothes.

27
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:16,850
She'll be here soon.

28
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,280
Look, everyone.

29
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,810
Ren Zhen, you look so beautiful today.

30
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:38,400
I saw you on the road just now,

31
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:41,000
and thought you were a fairy from the mountain.

32
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:41,720
Yes.

33
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:44,780
You are the most beautiful flower on the grassland now.

34
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,079
I was adjusting my dress at home,

35
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:48,280
and it took some time.

36
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,600
Sorry I'm late.

37
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,360
Am I wearing it right?

38
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,360
I'm not making a fool of myself, right?

39
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:52,920
You look great.

40
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:55,000
Sister Ren Zhen, your dress is so pretty.

41
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,120
I want one too.

42
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,320
Little Ruozha, you're asking the wrong person.

43
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,640
The person who gave her the dress

44
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,720
is over there.

45
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:03,880
Secretary.

46
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:06,170
Why didn't you give me a set of clothes?

47
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,320
Ren Zhen came to our village

48
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:10,240
to contribute to the live streaming business.

49
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:12,080
It's also her first time celebrating the Corban Festival.

50
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,400
I'm giving her a new set of clothes on behalf of Xia Village.

51
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,120
Aunt Guli,

52
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,240
your new clothes

53
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,560
can be bought with the money from selling goji berries.

54
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,200
Okay.

55
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:21,040
The Secretary is very thoughtful.

56
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:23,240
We should all thank Ren Zhen.

57
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,240
No need.

58
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,480
Sister Ren Zhen, go have a seat.

59
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,840
Grandpa Bate, come,

60
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,260
let's raise a glass together.

61
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,720
Happy holiday!

62
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:37,960
Happy holiday!

63
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,760
Come, Ren Zhen.

64
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:43,890
- Dance with us.
- No.

65
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,000
- No.
- Come on.

66
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,880
I don't know how.

67
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,260
I'll teach you.

68
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,690
I really don't know how.

69
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,680
Go ahead, Sister Ren Zhen.

70
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:55,020
How about I teach you the Kara Zhorga?

71
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,160
Thank you.

72
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:04,360
You and Ren Zhen are a perfect match.

73
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,720
Simply a couple.

74
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,480
You are both single, right?

75
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,360
Stay here

76
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:11,120
and be the bride and groom of Xia Village, okay?

77
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,440
Stay and settle down.

78
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,880
Stop joking around.

79
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,250
Stop joking around.

80
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,480
Secretary, you look quite happy.

81
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,760
Come dance with us.

82
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:23,640
Come.

83
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:24,680
Come.

84
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:26,080
Come, Ren Zhen.

85
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,800
I won't dance, you guys go ahead.

86
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:28,800
You guys go ahead.

87
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,160
What's wrong?

88
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,060
Miss your grandpa?

89
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,640
It's very sweet.

90
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:24,680
I should have been more thoughtful.

91
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:27,440
When I gave you the red envelope today,

92
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:29,240
I felt you were not in a good mood.

93
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:32,440
Uncle Yin, it has nothing to do with you.

94
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,480
My grandpa loved me just like you do.

95
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,080
No matter how old I get,

96
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,360
every Spring Festival,

97
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:41,360
he would prepare lucky money for me.

98
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,120
But since he passed away,

99
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,300
I never received it again.

100
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,600
If you can't let it go,

101
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:54,010
how can your grandpa rest in peace?

102
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:56,440
It's been seven years.

103
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:03,010
I dreamed of my grandpa last night.

104
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,130
He told me to go home.

105
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,840
I felt terrible after waking up.

106
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,250
I can't go back anymore.

107
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,480
How could that be?

108
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:17,720
Actually, you have changed a bit recently.

109
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,720
Xiacun is great,

110
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:22,840
and the people are nice.

111
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:28,480
What you want in your heart,

112
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,480
you can look for it here.

113
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,490
Don't be afraid,

114
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,760
and don't run away.

115
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,740
Uncle Yin, I've thought about it.

116
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:41,000
This is not where I belong.

117
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:44,880
I want to wait until the e-commerce business is stable.

118
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:45,880
Then I will leave.

119
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,760
Are you sure?

120
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,160
Secretary.

121
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,600
Secretary.

122
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,520
This isn't water.

123
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,160
You got the wrong one.

124
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,680
This is strong liquor brewed by Uncle Tuoka.

125
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,440
It doesn't burn your throat.

126
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,640
But it's very strong.

127
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,240
Secretary.

128
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:29,220
What's wrong with you?

129
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,520
Ren Zhen.

130
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,400
Secretary. Secretary.

131
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,240
Secretary.

132
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:37,320
Secretary.

133
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:39,799
Nazahai, let's fly together.
